comment_for_dlg2: Control functions for the same element must be\nlisted immediately one after another.\n(BlueM Bug 342)
The Identification of a dam must begin with a "T".\nThe TAL-file consists of several tables:\n1 as overview and 6 per element.
The maximum number of lines that can be entered\nper transport element is 26! (TRS_MAXSTZ)
